{"tid":1594161,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁美芬遭起底　資料被用作登記器官捐贈","createTime":"2019-09-25T12:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T07:54:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":806,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":138,"replies":[{"pid":"a56989202ac4f7b5a425596c60d912a55de31077","tid":1594161,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190925/photo/bkn-20190925185348930-0925_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190925194932\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190925%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190925185348930-0925_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190925194932&h=d8542d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網絡「起底」情況愈嚟愈嚴重，立法會議員梁美芬亦「中招」，唔單止個人資料被盜用，仲畀人冒認身份用咗嚟登記器官捐贈，佢已報警求助，亦同時通知衞生署同個人資料私隱專員公署。佢呼籲受害者企出嚟舉報，仲警告想進行「起底」嘅人勿以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n梁美芬話喺過去10年曾三度畀人盜用資料，一次收到銀行通知話有人冒認佢身份攞錢，好彩損失唔多，今次就係有友好將資料上載到通訊群組話畀佢知，佢嘅住址、身份證號碼同電話號碼慘被公開，並且有人冒認佢填寫個人資料，做一啲冇經佢同意嘅事，由於器官捐贈係一種承諾，同法律約束力有關，冒認佢填報已涉及刑事罪行，佢覺得事態嚴重，所以一定要報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n被問及追查到「元兇」嘅機會有幾多？佢認為警方有能力追查到「起底」嘅人，如果「起底」行為喺境外發生，反映涉案人士掌握好多公眾人物嘅資料，但點都會有線索追查到。<br />\n<br />\n佢又話根據香港法例第177章《人事登記條例》，偽造及冒用他人身份資料，一經定罪最高可被判罰款10萬港元及監禁10年，又話依家「起底」愈嚟愈多，參與嘅人可謂為所欲為，佢強調唔好以為喺網上就唔使理後果，同樣都要為行為負上民事同刑事責任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190925/mobile/bkn-20190925185348930-0925_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"268806597632c269b613b06b55132a15993c5c96","tid":1594161,"uid":212626,"like":506,"dislike":2,"score":504,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"老鼠器官<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b369d0e6bac096285306e6c606a6c4c8eb05df7","tid":1594161,"uid":277054,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:06:07.000Z","msg":"#五大訴求缺一不可 <br />\n#還我自由釋放義士<br />\n#沒有暴徒只有暴政 <br />\n#香港警察知法犯法<br />\n#還我雙真普選<br />\n<br />\n#光復香港時代革命 <br />\n#香港人加油 <br />\n#逃犯條例<br />\n#反送中<br />\n#noextraditiontochina <br />\n#antielabhk"},{"pid":"7b285d7bb42ce07b70038c9d16fbf5f7c3108a0c","tid":1594161,"uid":43327,"like":187,"dislike":1,"score":186,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"你死你事呀，唔想要你D心肝脾肺腎呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b3943370354e087143b06a1d95c539c50cb836","tid":1594161,"uid":18411,"like":298,"dislike":3,"score":295,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:06:43.000Z","msg":"反口就反口啦<br />\n扮被登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227ffdeea78af236c5e5bdb24128af95ff037efc","tid":1594161,"uid":184679,"like":551,"dislike":1,"score":550,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.cwcc.edu.hk/new/public/modules/subject/bio/2011-11-10-s7/album/slides/201111101765.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cwcc.edu.hk%2Fnew%2Fpublic%2Fmodules%2Fsubject%2Fbio%2F2011-11-10-s7%2Falbum%2Fslides%2F201111101765.jpg&h=c1f3a102&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31d3c9544979b2f088fa7ba4a0e2d213ad760c92","tid":1594161,"uid":25213,"like":365,"dislike":1,"score":364,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:08:21.000Z","msg":"即係鼠王芬唔支持器官捐贈？"},{"pid":"77a163ebfac69bedb6fe244faf45ca0ea8df3bd9","tid":1594161,"uid":134226,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"quote":{"pid":"46b3943370354e087143b06a1d95c539c50cb836","tid":1594161,"uid":18411,"like":298,"dislike":3,"score":295,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:06:43.000Z","msg":"反口就反口啦<br />\n扮被登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"係咪即係話佢本身都冇登記<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed51ae63ab4270f825410be7a82415e95777b28","tid":1594161,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77a163ebfac69bedb6fe244faf45ca0ea8df3bd9","tid":1594161,"uid":134226,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"quote":{"pid":"46b3943370354e087143b06a1d95c539c50cb836","tid":1594161,"uid":18411,"like":298,"dislike":3,"s